json.des: Array of U.S. Army enlisted Military Occupational Specialties (MOS) with description, Armed Services Vocational Aptitude Battery (ASVAB) composite (line) scores, and source of information. Note: ASVAB scores are contained in the "asv" array in the following order of line scores: [ GT, CL, CO, EL, FA, GM, MM, OF, SC, ST ]. Alternate scores for MOS with alternate score qualifications are contained in the "alt" array in the same order of line scores. The list is current as of 2023-07-20.
